==Description==

The [[Image:Part_RefineShape.svg|24px]] '''Part RefineShape''' command creates [[Glossary#Parametric|parametric]] copies with a refined shape from selected objects. It removes unnecessary edges from planar and cylindrical faces.

[[File:PartRefineShape_it.png]]
